name: KeyFi
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en:
KeyFi is an app-based platform for managing decentralized finance (DeFi).  
Manage your assets across multiple protocols, including Compound, Aave and others. With the KeyFi app users can swap, stake, rebalance, deposit and withdraw their assets all from one platform.

KeyFi Core allows users to view your wallet balances by connecting to MetaMask, WalletConnect, or SelfKey wallets.  Swap, stake, lend, and borrow assets across multiple DeFi platforms.  Find the best interest rates quickly and conveniently using our Rebalancer tool and earn exclusive KEYFI rewards through staking and liquidity mining.

KeyFi Pro (coming soon) will offer everything available in KeyFi, plus access to CeFi platforms such as Nexo.  Unlimited, custom portfolio alerts to Telegram, email, and SMS.  Discover new tokens and platforms curated by our unique algorithm and have innovative data visualizations powered by our data lake.
